TO SHOW AND TO TELL |SUM_TO_N| CALLED FOR |N|
    |TOTAL| PLACED AS 0.
    |I| PLACED AS 1.
    OVER AND OVER |I| TO BE DIMINISHED BY |N| WITH OR WITHOUT |I| AS IS |N|
        |TOTAL| PLACED AS |TOTAL| PUT TOGETHER |I|.
        |I| PLACED AS |I| PUT TOGETHER 1.
    END OVER
    RETURN PLACED AS |TOTAL|.
END SHOW

|RESULT| PLACED AS |SUM_TO_N| CALLED FOR 10.
PRESENTED AS |RESULT| TO THE RECEIVER.
